costroid budget
scope: API-lane spend this month (50% of month elapsed)
codex: ~$60.00 / ~$50.00 budget (120%) !! OVER, over by ~$10.00
  pace: 120% used vs 50% of month elapsed (over budget)
total (all tools): ~$84.00 / ~$100.00 budget (84%) ! near budget
  pace: 84% used vs 50% of month elapsed (ahead of pace)
claude-code: ~$15.00 / ~$60.00 budget (25%)
  pace: 25% used vs 50% of month elapsed (on track)
cursor: flat-fee subscription - no $ budget applies (not API-billed)
figures are local estimates (your tokens x current prices); run `costroid reconcile` to compare against the provider invoice.
